data.description: This adorable cottage is a nature lovers delight and creates an inviting and airy atmosphere with soaring ceilings and expansive sun soaked windows. The focal point of the home is a spiral staircase which adds a unique flair to the space.  The main level features an open-concept layout, seamlessly connecting the living area and kitchen to the full bath and second bedroom. Retreat to the upper-level loft for the primary bedroom, a space to relax and wake up to views of the beautiful Moodus reservoir. A wood stove for chilly nights and central air in the summer. A short walk away is the association's private beach to enjoy the sun, a swim, kayak ride, or just take in the wildlife. This beautiful property would make a wonderful first home, vacation retreat, or a short-term rental. The large yard is perfect for outside time and a garage and full basement offer plentiful storage. Don't miss your chance to own this one-of-a-kind home or vacation retreat! Subject to seller securing suitable housing.
